535
00:26:54,587 --> 00:26:57,210
- Oh, that sucks.
- Tell me about it.

536
00:26:57,248 --> 00:26:59,561
How about one more
game before you leave?

537
00:27:00,445 --> 00:27:01,710
All right.

538
00:27:02,945 --> 00:27:05,540
Good news.
Marc found us a town car.

539
00:27:05,575 --> 00:27:07,773
- Oh, great.
- You look familiar.

540
00:27:07,805 --> 00:27:09,722
- Have we met?
