kind of a turn-on.

604
00:30:41,025 --> 00:30:42,963
The Chin likes remorse.

605
00:30:45,638 --> 00:30:49,002
I am sad. I am so sad.

606
00:30:49,036 --> 00:30:51,251
Shh. Don't talk.
