me like my father did,

655
00:34:25,467 --> 00:34:26,533
but he didn't.

656
00:34:26,566 --> 00:34:28,730
Uh, okay,
now you're making me nervous.

657
00:34:29,088 --> 00:34:31,692
You are going to fire Daniel

658
00:34:31,727 --> 00:34:33,810
