that I'm sorry.

673
00:35:19,398 --> 00:35:21,130
At least let me pay
for your pretzel.

674
00:35:21,167 --> 00:35:23,011
No, I don't want
anything from you.

675
00:35:24,165 --> 00:35:25,633
Okay, a dollar.

676
00:35:26,678 --> 00:35:29,183
- Thank you.
- You're... welcome.

677
00:35:30,286 --> 00:35:32,601
