I know you like extra mustard--

678
00:35:32,635 --> 00:35:35,710
Listen, Walter and
I--it wasn't about you.

679
00:35:35,988 --> 00:35:38,493
I broke up with him because I
wasn't in love with him anymore,

680
00:35:38,526 --> 00:35:40,652
