00:36:40,078 --> 00:36:41,171
Henry!

692
00:36:41,686 --> 00:36:42,740
Charlie?

693
00:36:42,777 --> 00:36:44,533
- Charlie!
- Betty!

694
00:36:49,435 --> 00:36:50,901
