695
00:36:50,938 --> 00:36:53,301
Oh, that subway ride rocked!

696
00:36:53,377 --> 00:36:55,783
People are so nice
in this city!

697
00:36:55,838 --> 00:36:58,082
There was this one guy--he
kind of touched my butt,

698
00:36:58,116 --> 00:37:00,953
