758
00:40:02,876 --> 00:40:05,432
No! Claire?

759
00:40:05,805 --> 00:40:06,763
Claire!

760
00:40:10,218 --> 00:40:11,263
Claire!

761
00:40:16,257 --> 00:40:17,290
Claire.

762
00:40:22,315 --> 00:40:24,700
